    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1274700/extras/e32fced1a5913aa6014ec95f85cb7223.avif?t=1772023972\" width=1500 height=250 /></span><strong><i>You Alone Can Defeat Evil</i></strong>（YACDE）是一款以单一无情Boss战—<strong>大恶魔</strong>—为核心的高难度动作挑战。<br>每一次死亡都是一堂课，每一次尝试都让你更接近掌握技巧的巅峰。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >扮演被<strong>埃斯基隆教团</strong>流放的流浪巫师，面对一个专门考验你的耐心、精准和决心的敌人。<br>这不是一场靠运气的战斗，而是一场关于学习、适应和执行力的较量。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >手握禁忌魔法，身负诅咒纹身，每一次尝试都成为生存之战。<br>死亡不可避免，但绝非毫无意义。<br>每一次失败都会解锁新的力量，揭示隐藏的秘密，并让你再次优化策略，克服看似不可能的挑战。另一次适应的机会。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1274700/extras/40512a39acb5a834d46e5f6de7aaf1f7.avif?t=1772023972\" width=1500 height=250 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1274700/extras/e7bb6c140a1d7a7972138f4be7c1bdd9.poster.avif?t=1772023972\" width=1170 height=498 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1274700/extras/e7bb6c140a1d7a7972138f4be7c1bdd9.webm?t=1772023972\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1274700/extras/e7bb6c140a1d7a7972138f4be7c1bdd9.mp4?t=1772023972\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1274700/extras/fcae8575309cc86c774529911ef6972e.avif?t=1772023972\" width=1500 height=250 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>面对伟大恶魔！</strong><br>进入无情的Boss战，每一次动作都至关重要，唯有精通才能决定命运。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>释放禁忌魔法！</strong><br>利用扭曲灵魂的纹身获得新能力，打造属于你的战斗风格。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>如影般移动！</strong><br>在基于动作的流畅战斗系统中闪避、穿梭和攻击，精准迅速。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>死而更强！</strong><br>每次死亡都会在身体上刻下新纹身，使你更强、更智慧，更接近胜利。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>发现隐藏的故事！</strong><br>获得神秘的Lore书籍，揭示埃斯基隆的失落历史，并赋予新的魔法能力。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>探索黑暗秘密！</strong><br>揭开隐藏机制和神秘元素，超越单人游戏体验。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>挑战极限！</strong><br>凭借残酷的难度和技能导向设计，YACDE为追求真正挑战的玩家而生。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>你能击败伟大恶魔吗？还是会成为埃斯基隆废墟中又一个被遗忘的灵魂？</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1274700/extras/894adb910b665806ab0187ce7526d38e.poster.avif?t=1772023972\" width=1170 height=498 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1274700/extras/894adb910b665806ab0187ce7526d38e.webm?t=1772023972\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1274700/extras/894adb910b665806ab0187ce7526d38e.mp4?t=1772023972\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这不是一款第一次尝试就能获胜的游戏。<br>它关于坚持、成长，以及争取每一寸进展。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >大恶魔不会等待。<br>他不会手下留情。<br>也不会宽恕你的错误。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1274700/extras/3fb9bebb1ec6d5aa042065faeab14b21.poster.avif?t=1772023972\" width=1170 height=498 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1274700/extras/3fb9bebb1ec6d5aa042065faeab14b21.webm?t=1772023972\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1274700/extras/3fb9bebb1ec6d5aa042065faeab14b21.mp4?t=1772023972\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但凭借足够的技巧、耐心和决心……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>只有你，才能击败邪恶。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
